  "reference_number": "GAC0053",
  "remarks": "\nAivars LEMBERGS is an involved person under the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis of the following grounds: LEMBERGS is or has been involved in (1) being responsible for or engaging in serious corruption Specifically, LEMBERGS, whilst mayor of Ventspils, has been responsible for or has engaged in serious corruption by way of bribery and the misappropriation of property.\n",
